WEBVTT

00:00:22.920 --> 00:00:24.850
I want to negotiate a deal with you.

00:00:25.960 --> 00:00:26.890
Can these things

00:00:27.320 --> 00:00:27.960
Be made?

00:00:28.440 --> 00:00:30.370
I need them the day after tomorrow.

00:00:31.070 --> 00:00:32.670
Do you think I'm omnipotent?

00:00:33.070 --> 00:00:35.600
Signal arrows, fire thunderstone, and sleeve daggers.

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:36.430
You think these things

00:00:36.430 --> 00:00:37.880
Can be conjured up just like that?

00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:40.520
You and Yuan Xiaoliu can make it in time.

00:00:44.070 --> 00:00:45.600
I'll pay extra. Double.

00:00:49.670 --> 00:00:50.560
Triple.

00:00:50.880 --> 00:00:52.210
I can't afford any more.

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:55.070
Discussing money between friends makes things awkward.

00:00:55.070 --> 00:00:56.670
You know what I want the most.

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:02.600
Alright, I promise you.

00:01:03.240 --> 00:01:05.560
Li Lejun won't be chosen for a political marriage.

00:01:05.560 --> 00:01:06.120
Deal.

00:01:11.310 --> 00:01:12.950
Are these the places you and Yizhi

00:01:12.950 --> 00:01:14.350
Want to travel to in the future?

00:01:14.350 --> 00:01:16.610
Yes, these are all places I want to visit.

00:01:16.710 --> 00:01:17.789
Master Yuan told me

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.400
There are special ores

00:01:19.400 --> 00:01:20.730
In some of these places.

00:01:20.920 --> 00:01:22.400
It sounds very interesting.

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:23.530
I want to take a look.

00:01:27.590 --> 00:01:29.000
Here, here,

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:30.010
And here.

00:01:30.500 --> 00:01:32.960
There are bandits at the border. Be careful.

00:01:33.590 --> 00:01:35.039
If it's convenient for you,

00:01:35.039 --> 00:01:37.200
You can tell me the route you are going to take.

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.350
There is a geomancer in the army,

00:01:38.350 --> 00:01:39.810
Who can draw a detailed map

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:41.170
To avoid any omissions.

00:01:41.479 --> 00:01:42.310
Xiao Wuyi,

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:43.640
Having you as a friend

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.700
Is a true treasure.

00:01:46.070 --> 00:01:46.710
Then when the time comes,

00:01:46.710 --> 00:01:48.200
Can I also use your name

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:49.860
To stay in the Beifu Army Camp?

00:01:52.070 --> 00:01:52.930
In your dreams.

00:01:53.310 --> 00:01:54.920
You are not a military family member.

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:57.520
Don't even think about taking advantage of me.

00:03:25.920 --> 00:03:29.840
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

00:03:30.079 --> 00:03:32.730
[Episode 11]

00:03:33.840 --> 00:03:34.430
Wuyi.

00:03:37.710 --> 00:03:38.750
Congratulations.

00:03:38.750 --> 00:03:40.410
You had a great victory today.

00:03:41.750 --> 00:03:42.560
How is Da?

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:43.750
He was injured by an arrow,

00:03:43.750 --> 00:03:45.030
But his life is not in danger.

00:03:45.030 --> 00:03:46.030
He made contributions in this battle.

00:03:46.030 --> 00:03:48.079
His Majesty has agreed to transfer him to the Imperial Guard.

00:03:48.079 --> 00:03:49.740
He will be back by my side soon.

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:51.290
That's good.

00:03:55.120 --> 00:03:56.650
When did you start planning

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.760
The matter of Heximu?

00:04:00.150 --> 00:04:01.880
Before returning to Jiankang.

00:04:04.830 --> 00:04:06.020
That's our Wuyi,

00:04:06.430 --> 00:04:07.840
Never missing a single detail.

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:08.900
Now, the Eagle King

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:10.000
Has also been forced by you

00:04:10.000 --> 00:04:11.730
To sit down and have a good talk.

00:04:16.800 --> 00:04:17.430
Wuyi.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.959
If I want to contend with you,

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:23.220
Do I have the qualifications?

00:04:39.310 --> 00:04:41.510
The Eagle King bet the three prefectures,

00:04:41.510 --> 00:04:42.970
And I bet the name of Beifu.

00:04:43.310 --> 00:04:44.770
What are you fighting for?

00:04:45.270 --> 00:04:46.159
What is the bet?

00:04:47.040 --> 00:04:47.770
I don't know.

00:04:49.270 --> 00:04:50.560
Perhaps after a fight,

00:04:51.270 --> 00:04:52.330
I will understand.

00:05:11.870 --> 00:05:14.600
I saw everything in the martial arts arena today.

00:05:14.750 --> 00:05:15.870
You like Xie Jiayu?

00:05:23.070 --> 00:05:23.720
Yes.

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:25.620
You are shameless.

00:05:25.630 --> 00:05:27.690
Before I knew she was the one you love,

00:05:28.510 --> 00:05:30.720
I had fallen in love with Xie Jiayu at first sight.

00:05:30.720 --> 00:05:32.180
But you are my best friend.

00:05:32.390 --> 00:05:33.270
And now you know.

00:05:33.270 --> 00:05:34.730
So I have done nothing now.

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:38.130
She is still waiting to leave with you.

00:05:41.040 --> 00:05:43.000
You're the one who doesn't want to leave.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:43.950
So what if I am?

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:47.560
I'm betting Xie Jiayu

00:05:48.310 --> 00:05:49.480
On this arrow.

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:53.760
Xie Jiayu is a person.

00:05:54.040 --> 00:05:55.070
She has feelings

00:05:55.070 --> 00:05:56.200
And a life of her own.

00:05:56.310 --> 00:05:57.600
She shouldn't sacrifice for anyone

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:59.130
Or be controlled by anyone.

00:06:00.070 --> 00:06:00.750
Yizhi,

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.450
You told me this yourself.

00:06:11.430 --> 00:06:12.760
Whether to stay or leave

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:14.630
Is up to you.

00:06:25.310 --> 00:06:27.170
Whether Xie Jiayu stays or leaves

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:28.870
Is up to her as well.

00:07:03.430 --> 00:07:04.430
Ziqi.

00:07:16.750 --> 00:07:19.880
I remember you've liked sour food since you were little.

00:07:20.430 --> 00:07:22.630
These sour plum cakes are made

00:07:22.630 --> 00:07:23.680
From fresh seasonal plums.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:24.390
Try some.

00:07:28.600 --> 00:07:29.270
How is it?

00:07:30.310 --> 00:07:31.430
When I was in the army,

00:07:31.430 --> 00:07:32.750
I missed your cooking.

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:35.870
Next,

00:07:36.680 --> 00:07:37.830
What are your plans?

00:07:38.159 --> 00:07:40.040
Now that the three prefectures are settled,

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:41.510
My peace talks with Northern Qin are still ongoing—

00:07:41.510 --> 00:07:43.120
Who asked about the peace talks?

00:07:43.120 --> 00:07:46.120
I'm asking about your marriage.

00:07:47.700 --> 00:07:48.960
My proposal for reform

00:07:49.120 --> 00:07:50.159
Touches the interests of noble families.

00:07:50.159 --> 00:07:51.270
The Empress Dowager hasn't declared her stance,

00:07:51.270 --> 00:07:52.630
But she'll definitely have misgivings about the marriage

00:07:52.630 --> 00:07:53.630
Between the He and Xiao families.

00:07:53.630 --> 00:07:54.890
When the time is right,

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.630
I will end this marriage

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:58.480
And give He Yuanji her freedom,

00:07:58.480 --> 00:08:00.210
-so that she and Yao can— -Wuyi.

00:08:00.680 --> 00:08:01.750
What I mean is,

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.420
Life is a long journey.

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:04.610
Walking hand in hand

00:08:05.040 --> 00:08:06.680
Beats going alone.

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:10.720
I really don't want you

00:08:11.120 --> 00:08:12.120
To be truly alone.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:17.290
When you fell off your horse and fell into a coma that day,

00:08:17.320 --> 00:08:18.510
Jiayu came to me

00:08:19.190 --> 00:08:20.850
And told me to be fairer to you.

00:08:22.360 --> 00:08:24.600
Although she doesn't know the whole story,

00:08:24.600 --> 00:08:26.660
She can still see your difficulties.

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:29.510
I can see she's a good girl,

00:08:30.120 --> 00:08:32.110
And she cares for you.

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:36.320
Xie Jiayu is pure and kind-hearted,

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:39.480
But she already has someone she likes.

00:08:39.840 --> 00:08:40.750
So what?

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:43.039
Even if she's a kite in someone else's hands,

00:08:43.039 --> 00:08:44.010
If you like her,

00:08:44.960 --> 00:08:46.960
What's the harm in fighting for her?

00:08:47.270 --> 00:08:50.320
Besides, you now hold the string.

00:08:50.550 --> 00:08:52.840
In terms of status, you lose to no one.

00:08:53.120 --> 00:08:55.510
Are you telling me to snatch her?

00:08:55.530 --> 00:08:56.770
You're a grown man.

00:08:57.870 --> 00:08:59.550
What's the harm in fighting for her?

00:08:59.550 --> 00:09:01.350
But I promised Princess Yunzhao

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:03.320
To give Xie Jiayu the freedom to choose.

00:09:03.320 --> 00:09:06.080
You've met Princess Yunzhao?

00:09:06.390 --> 00:09:07.750
For the path I must take,

00:09:08.580 --> 00:09:10.980
I've already dragged the Xiao family down.

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:13.330
I don't want to implicate anyone else.

00:09:13.910 --> 00:09:14.480
Darling!

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:16.630
I caught a big fish!

00:09:17.270 --> 00:09:18.440
Your son is useless.

00:09:18.550 --> 00:09:20.350
He didn't even catch half a fish.

00:09:21.750 --> 00:09:23.080
Your father is really

00:09:23.270 --> 00:09:24.330
Naughty by nature.

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:36.830
Come on.

00:09:41.910 --> 00:09:43.170
Let me refill your cup.

00:09:43.790 --> 00:09:44.240
Okay.

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:45.780
I'll fill mine too.

00:09:46.510 --> 00:09:49.910
Yuezhou, one of the three prefectures awarded in this competition,

00:09:49.910 --> 00:09:53.270
Is where my husband died in battle.

00:09:53.600 --> 00:09:55.460
Ruisheng, I've heard you say this

00:09:56.000 --> 00:09:58.200
3 times already.

00:10:00.240 --> 00:10:01.480
I'm just happy.

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:04.220
If his spirit in heaven

00:10:04.960 --> 00:10:07.020
Knew that Yuezhou had returned to Ye,

00:10:08.360 --> 00:10:09.630
He would be thrilled.

00:10:09.870 --> 00:10:12.270
Then Ruisheng, was your husband

00:10:12.390 --> 00:10:14.270
Handsome?

00:10:14.440 --> 00:10:15.440
Of course.

00:10:16.360 --> 00:10:18.400
Otherwise, why would I have chosen him?

00:10:18.400 --> 00:10:21.200
He couldn't even afford the betrothal gifts then.

00:10:22.000 --> 00:10:24.550
Is your man handsome?

00:10:24.870 --> 00:10:26.960
Right, is he handsome?

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:36.040
I understand.

00:10:37.790 --> 00:10:39.450
If you think about it that way,

00:10:39.870 --> 00:10:41.400
Xiao Wuyi is quite pitiful.

00:10:41.480 --> 00:10:42.880
He is so good at fighting.

00:10:42.960 --> 00:10:44.480
But he’s been married 3 times.

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:45.750
And no one wants him.

00:10:46.550 --> 00:10:47.960
-Coming. -Let me tell you.

00:10:47.960 --> 00:10:50.270
-He has a bad temper. -Let's go, Ziqi. Let's play in the water.

00:10:50.270 --> 00:10:52.670
-In fact, he is a good man. -Let's go, Ruisheng.

00:10:52.670 --> 00:10:54.670
It's just that his temper is too bad.

00:10:57.030 --> 00:10:57.790
Xie Jiayu,

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:00.380
What did you just say about me?

00:11:01.270 --> 00:11:03.200
Ruisheng, I... I'll also go...

00:11:03.390 --> 00:11:03.870
Go...

00:11:04.070 --> 00:11:05.070
Play in the water.

00:11:06.840 --> 00:11:08.110
Good. Very good.

00:11:08.750 --> 00:11:10.680
I've never seen such a good person.

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:14.650
What is this?

00:11:14.650 --> 00:11:16.750
This is Li Lejun's new Four Pillars of Destiny Chart.

00:11:16.750 --> 00:11:17.850
Whether from the perspective of Northern Qin

00:11:17.850 --> 00:11:20.080
Or Southern Ye's calendar and astrology,

00:11:20.080 --> 00:11:22.080
Hers and the Eagle King's are a sign of great misfortune.

00:11:22.080 --> 00:11:23.880
Put this in the royal genealogy.

00:11:24.030 --> 00:11:25.230
I hope it can help her.

00:11:25.360 --> 00:11:26.910
Okay, thanks.

00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:29.550
I've only been married once.

00:11:29.550 --> 00:11:31.480
I don't need your pity.

00:11:33.840 --> 00:11:34.550
I

00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:36.480
Do have a bad temper.

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:38.790
No.

00:11:45.750 --> 00:11:46.360
These are

00:11:46.360 --> 00:11:48.690
My ideas for upgrading the Beifu weapons.

00:11:48.910 --> 00:11:50.270
Some are already perfected,

00:11:50.270 --> 00:11:51.670
And some still need work.

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:52.840
On the day of the Double Ninth Ceremony,

00:11:52.840 --> 00:11:54.000
I promised the Beifu soldiers

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:55.460
To upgrade their weapons.

00:11:55.790 --> 00:11:57.450
I will never break my promise.

00:11:58.600 --> 00:11:59.120
Well...

00:11:59.650 --> 00:12:01.600
Most of the designs are whimsical.

00:12:02.170 --> 00:12:03.500
But the talent is there.

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:06.030
Why don't you come with me to Beifu?

00:12:06.030 --> 00:12:07.390
Designing weapons

00:12:07.510 --> 00:12:09.270
Is different from constructing mechanisms.

00:12:09.270 --> 00:12:11.240
It requires examining the local terrain,

00:12:11.240 --> 00:12:12.670
Weather, and tactics.

00:12:12.670 --> 00:12:13.360
Stop.

00:12:14.670 --> 00:12:16.030
I want to leave Xiao Wuyi,

00:12:16.030 --> 00:12:17.150
Not be sold to him.

00:12:17.550 --> 00:12:20.390
Besides, you just want to trick me into the Directorate of Military Equipment,

00:12:20.390 --> 00:12:22.450
So you can slack off yourself, right?

00:12:22.630 --> 00:12:23.550
You.

00:12:23.960 --> 00:12:25.390
You are just like your mother.

00:12:25.390 --> 00:12:27.510
You keep saying you want to roam the martial arts world

00:12:27.510 --> 00:12:29.150
And wander to the ends of the earth.

00:12:29.150 --> 00:12:31.750
Then let me ask you, where is the martial arts world?

00:12:31.750 --> 00:12:33.480
And where are the ends of the earth?

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:34.220
-Martial arts world... -Look,

00:12:34.220 --> 00:12:35.150
You can't answer, can you?

00:12:35.150 --> 00:12:36.950
You just want to travel and play.

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:38.030
Let me tell you.

00:12:38.440 --> 00:12:39.720
At this time of year,

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:42.840
Heading south, there are rainstorms and floods.

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:44.630
Heading north, there are sandstorms.

00:12:44.630 --> 00:12:46.550
Heading west, there are high mountains and steep hills.

00:12:46.550 --> 00:12:47.610
Most importantly,

00:12:47.910 --> 00:12:50.310
Bandit rebellions occur from time to time.

00:12:51.030 --> 00:12:52.240
Still, I shouldn't be scared

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:53.440
Before I even go, right?

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:54.170
That's true.

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:58.360
Why don't you take me as your master?

00:12:58.360 --> 00:12:59.550
I'll take you to see

00:12:59.550 --> 00:13:01.080
The desert roses

00:13:01.270 --> 00:13:02.720
And yellow phosphorus mines you like.

00:13:02.720 --> 00:13:03.780
Most importantly,

00:13:03.840 --> 00:13:04.550
As your master, I

00:13:04.550 --> 00:13:06.120
Will pass on everything I've learned

00:13:06.120 --> 00:13:07.270
In my life to you,

00:13:07.910 --> 00:13:09.030
Making your mechanism designs

00:13:09.030 --> 00:13:11.690
Benefit the people's livelihood in the future.

00:13:12.030 --> 00:13:12.550
Then...

00:13:13.320 --> 00:13:14.850
Can I bring a family member?

00:13:16.150 --> 00:13:18.150
I won't ask who this person is first.

00:13:18.790 --> 00:13:19.840
Is he willing?

00:13:20.390 --> 00:13:21.360
As a dignified man,

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:23.030
Doesn't he have his own ambitions?

00:13:23.030 --> 00:13:23.550
He...

00:13:45.440 --> 00:13:46.320
Picking a wife?

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:49.750
Thanks.

00:13:52.440 --> 00:13:54.600
That Xie girl is so quick to catch on.

00:13:55.150 --> 00:13:56.880
After some persuasion from me,

00:13:56.910 --> 00:13:58.720
She's already tempted

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:00.720
By the idea of becoming my disciple.

00:14:01.350 --> 00:14:01.960
Also,

00:14:02.150 --> 00:14:04.360
What amazing luck you have.

00:14:04.790 --> 00:14:05.850
To have the heavens

00:14:05.960 --> 00:14:07.750
Send you such a treasure.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:14.040
Do you look familiar?

00:14:14.910 --> 00:14:15.790
Caltrop fireball.

00:14:15.790 --> 00:14:18.630
Xie tinkered with this herself

00:14:18.630 --> 00:14:19.910
After reading ancient books.

00:14:19.910 --> 00:14:21.480
It perfectly matches

00:14:21.480 --> 00:14:22.940
My previous design ideas.

00:14:23.200 --> 00:14:24.270
Such talent

00:14:24.630 --> 00:14:26.200
Indeed shouldn't be buried

00:14:26.200 --> 00:14:28.260
In the romance of the inner quarters.

00:14:29.200 --> 00:14:31.000
You've really found a treasure.

00:14:35.670 --> 00:14:38.190
[Divorce Agreement]

00:14:41.390 --> 00:14:42.630
You like Xie Jiayu?

00:14:43.910 --> 00:14:44.440
Yes.

00:14:45.240 --> 00:14:47.100
Whether Xie Jiayu stays or leaves

00:14:47.240 --> 00:14:48.360
Is up to her as well.

00:14:56.150 --> 00:14:58.530
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

00:14:59.750 --> 00:15:02.200
Her Majesty has selected some princesses for you, Your Highness.

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:04.960
This is the legitimate daughter of Lord Liu, Vice Censor-in-Chief.

00:15:04.960 --> 00:15:05.790
She is 15.

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:07.270
She is well-versed in poetry and books,

00:15:07.270 --> 00:15:08.910
And is best at playing the guqin.

00:15:08.910 --> 00:15:11.960
This one is the niece of Lord Zhao, Director of the Secretariat.

00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:12.960
She has practiced martial arts since childhood.

00:15:12.960 --> 00:15:13.960
She has a valiant temperament,

00:15:13.960 --> 00:15:15.560
Truly a heroine among women.

00:15:18.360 --> 00:15:18.870
Lejun.

00:15:20.120 --> 00:15:20.550
Come.

00:15:22.840 --> 00:15:24.390
Do you think Yaoyao prefers moon white

00:15:24.390 --> 00:15:25.320
Or azure?

00:15:25.550 --> 00:15:27.630
Let's wait for her to choose for herself.

00:15:27.630 --> 00:15:28.200
Brother.

00:15:28.480 --> 00:15:30.680
She usually likes to study those tools.

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:32.030
But the palace has many rules,

00:15:32.030 --> 00:15:33.030
And it's not safe.

00:15:33.080 --> 00:15:35.880
I'm afraid it will be hard for her to enjoy herself.

00:15:36.440 --> 00:15:38.640
She also likes to listen to storybooks.

00:15:38.960 --> 00:15:40.030
We can keep some entertainers

00:15:40.030 --> 00:15:41.030
To make her happy.

00:15:41.750 --> 00:15:42.910
As for the Imperial Cuisine Department,

00:15:42.910 --> 00:15:44.270
I also sent someone to adjust

00:15:44.270 --> 00:15:46.130
The menus according to her taste.

00:15:46.570 --> 00:15:47.550
Hurry and help me think

00:15:47.550 --> 00:15:48.790
If there's anything else I've missed.

00:15:48.790 --> 00:15:49.390
Brother,

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:50.770
Does Yaoyao know

00:15:51.080 --> 00:15:52.840
That you don't plan to leave Jiankang

00:15:52.840 --> 00:15:55.240
But still want to bring her into the palace?

00:15:55.480 --> 00:15:56.870
As long as I can be with her,

00:15:56.870 --> 00:15:58.930
What difference does it make whether we leave Jiankang or not?

00:15:58.930 --> 00:16:00.790
How could there be no difference?

00:16:01.440 --> 00:16:02.970
Yaoyao yearns for freedom,

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:05.150
But you want her to live in the deep palace for a long time.

00:16:05.150 --> 00:16:06.410
Don't you understand?

00:16:06.550 --> 00:16:08.390
Yaoyao can give up the name of Xie Jiayu

00:16:08.390 --> 00:16:09.840
To travel the world with you.

00:16:09.840 --> 00:16:11.550
But she won't give up the name of Xie Jiayu

00:16:11.550 --> 00:16:12.720
To enter the palace with you.

00:16:12.720 --> 00:16:14.960
Besides, there are these women.

00:16:15.960 --> 00:16:17.760
These are all stopgap measures.

00:16:18.600 --> 00:16:20.400
Yaoyao will surely understand.

00:16:21.230 --> 00:16:23.550
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

00:16:27.870 --> 00:16:28.960
Over the past few days, one after another,

00:16:28.960 --> 00:16:31.120
Prominent families have sent portraits to the Eastern Palace.

00:16:31.120 --> 00:16:32.670
It seems they intend to propose marriage.

00:16:32.670 --> 00:16:34.960
It looks like Prince Qi is determined not to leave.

00:16:34.960 --> 00:16:36.510
Lady Xie is still in the dark.

00:16:36.510 --> 00:16:37.670
These past few days, she's been busy preparing

00:16:37.670 --> 00:16:39.320
Parting gifts for everyone in the mansion.

00:16:39.320 --> 00:16:40.320
For the Heir's Consort,

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:41.390
It's a paperweight.

00:16:41.390 --> 00:16:42.200
For Madam Ruisheng,

00:16:42.200 --> 00:16:43.750
It's a brand-new set of acupuncture needles.

00:16:43.750 --> 00:16:44.840
For the Prince and the Princess,

00:16:44.840 --> 00:16:46.720
It's a suit of armor and a bladed hairpin.

00:16:46.720 --> 00:16:47.510
A single slash severs the throat.

00:16:47.510 --> 00:16:48.840
The fastest way to slaughter a chicken.

00:16:48.840 --> 00:16:49.790
For Ziqi, it's a stack of

00:16:49.790 --> 00:16:51.910
Classic books she hasn't even finished reading herself.

00:16:51.910 --> 00:16:52.510
That's it?

00:16:53.240 --> 00:16:55.440
Yan Yue and I got a pair of new shoes each.

00:16:56.960 --> 00:16:57.630
Calm down.

00:17:01.600 --> 00:17:02.460
Your Highness.

00:17:02.910 --> 00:17:04.069
The Eagle King suddenly went back on his word.

00:17:04.069 --> 00:17:06.270
He wants to add terms to the peace talks.

00:17:07.750 --> 00:17:09.640
If you interrupt my medical practice again,

00:17:09.640 --> 00:17:11.569
You will have to find someone else.

00:17:12.480 --> 00:17:13.880
He still hasn't given up.

00:17:14.510 --> 00:17:15.910
What are his conditions?

00:17:16.550 --> 00:17:17.150
What is it?

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:29.790
Leave us.

00:17:30.590 --> 00:17:31.160
Yes.

00:17:35.200 --> 00:17:35.750
Brother,

00:17:36.590 --> 00:17:37.450
What happened?

00:17:37.550 --> 00:17:40.440
Lejun, did you meet the Eagle King once?

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:41.790
Yes.

00:17:46.480 --> 00:17:48.170
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:17:48.170 --> 00:17:50.480
I thought he would make things difficult in public,

00:17:50.480 --> 00:17:52.350
But he didn't mention it later.

00:17:53.000 --> 00:17:54.790
I thought the poisoning matter

00:17:54.790 --> 00:17:56.440
Couldn't be brought out into the open.

00:17:56.440 --> 00:17:57.750
Her Majesty and the Eagle King

00:17:57.750 --> 00:17:59.340
Probably wouldn't do anything to me.

00:17:59.340 --> 00:18:00.590
So I was relieved.

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:02.880
Why? Is the Eagle King

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:04.480
Blackmailing you with this?

00:18:07.510 --> 00:18:09.440
The Eagle King intends to treat you as a princess

00:18:09.440 --> 00:18:10.960
For a political marriage with Northern Qin,

00:18:10.960 --> 00:18:12.720
To show the sincerity of the peace talks between the two countries.

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:13.590
What?

00:18:14.400 --> 00:18:15.600
Political marriage?

00:18:18.270 --> 00:18:18.880
Brother.

00:18:21.270 --> 00:18:23.240
Don't worry, I will protect you.

00:18:23.830 --> 00:18:26.290
I will never let you marry into Northern Qin.

00:18:29.010 --> 00:18:30.100
[Ziji Palace]

00:18:33.680 --> 00:18:35.440
This is the legitimate daughter of Minister Cao, Commandant of Justice.

00:18:35.440 --> 00:18:36.680
She knows 6 languages

00:18:37.160 --> 00:18:39.480
And can assist you with foreign affairs, Your Highness.

00:18:39.480 --> 00:18:42.350
This is the younger sister of the Left Palace Guard General.

00:18:42.350 --> 00:18:43.510
She is excellent at brewing tea.

00:18:43.510 --> 00:18:47.350
Upon tasting it, I find it surpasses the Nanzhao Xueya tea by quite a margin.

00:18:47.350 --> 00:18:48.160
It seems

00:18:48.920 --> 00:18:51.320
It's hard for you to find a good match today.

00:18:53.640 --> 00:18:56.440
He Tian, take everyone away.

00:18:57.310 --> 00:18:57.790
Yes.

00:18:59.110 --> 00:19:00.170
Take them all away.

00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:00.860
-Yes. -Yes.

00:19:08.110 --> 00:19:10.110
Sorry to trouble you, Your Majesty.

00:19:10.550 --> 00:19:11.350
It's nothing.

00:19:12.550 --> 00:19:15.400
Although I couldn't find a good match for you today,

00:19:15.400 --> 00:19:18.260
There is another excellent marriage arrangement.

00:19:24.310 --> 00:19:25.720
The day before yesterday,

00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:27.640
The Eagle King sent an envoy to the palace,

00:19:27.640 --> 00:19:30.720
Who said the Eagle King admires Princess Pingning's virtues,

00:19:30.720 --> 00:19:33.400
Is willing to offer the 1,000-li grassland in Monan as a betrothal gift,

00:19:33.400 --> 00:19:34.750
And use the etiquette for a royal princess

00:19:34.750 --> 00:19:37.150
To ask for the hand of your sister, Li Lejun.

00:19:37.480 --> 00:19:40.160
I think this is an excellent marriage arrangement,

00:19:40.160 --> 00:19:43.360
So I accepted the marriage document and betrothal gifts.

00:19:43.480 --> 00:19:44.540
Please take a look.

00:19:56.790 --> 00:19:59.750
Recently, Northern Qin and our Ye

00:19:59.750 --> 00:20:01.550
Are about to sign a peace treaty.

00:20:02.240 --> 00:20:03.200
Our people at Northern Border

00:20:03.200 --> 00:20:04.930
Will no longer suffer from war.

00:20:05.030 --> 00:20:06.830
If we can have a political marriage with Northern Qin,

00:20:06.830 --> 00:20:08.690
Wouldn't it be a blessing for our people

00:20:08.690 --> 00:20:09.820
And for Ye?

00:20:22.750 --> 00:20:25.110
Your Majesty, peace talks do not mean begging for peace.

00:20:25.110 --> 00:20:26.160
If we just keep yielding,

00:20:26.160 --> 00:20:27.640
It will only make Northern Qin more arrogant.

00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:29.160
Today, he dares to ask for my sister.

00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:31.560
Tomorrow, he will dare to ask for Jiankang.

00:20:32.680 --> 00:20:34.160
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

00:20:34.160 --> 00:20:35.030
Reconsider?

00:20:36.590 --> 00:20:37.830
If I reconsider,

00:20:38.140 --> 00:20:40.670
Princess Pingning will have left the palace!

00:20:51.680 --> 00:20:52.750
Bring her in!

00:20:53.240 --> 00:20:54.030
Bring her in.

00:20:56.940 --> 00:20:59.460
Today, I want to see

00:21:00.270 --> 00:21:02.880
Who dares to take Li Lejun away

00:21:03.270 --> 00:21:04.670
And ruin the peace talks.

00:21:10.720 --> 00:21:11.160
Lejun!

00:21:12.070 --> 00:21:12.590
Lejun!

00:21:13.760 --> 00:21:14.350
Brother.

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:25.010
Princess Pingning left the palace secretly,

00:21:25.240 --> 00:21:26.570
Ruining the peace talks

00:21:26.640 --> 00:21:28.570
And disregarding the safety of Ye.

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:29.730
Beat her!

00:21:32.070 --> 00:21:32.550
Lejun!

00:21:32.590 --> 00:21:33.390
Your Majesty!

00:21:34.030 --> 00:21:34.830
Your Majesty!

00:21:36.960 --> 00:21:37.760
Your Majesty!

00:21:37.960 --> 00:21:39.440
I was the one who didn't want Lejun to enter a political marriage.

00:21:39.440 --> 00:21:40.760
I was the one who sent someone to take her out of the palace.

00:21:40.760 --> 00:21:41.960
The one who should be beaten

00:21:41.960 --> 00:21:43.270
Should be me, Your Majesty!

00:21:43.270 --> 00:21:43.750
No,

00:21:44.200 --> 00:21:45.130
That's not true.

00:21:45.310 --> 00:21:48.240
Your Majesty, this has nothing to do with my brother.

00:21:48.270 --> 00:21:49.790
I didn't want to marry the Eagle King,

00:21:49.790 --> 00:21:50.920
So I ran away secretly.

00:21:50.920 --> 00:21:53.480
If you want to punish someone, punish me alone.

00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:54.940
Don't involve my brother.

00:21:55.200 --> 00:21:55.750
Lejun.

00:21:55.750 --> 00:21:56.350
Brother.

00:21:57.310 --> 00:21:58.240
I know

00:21:58.830 --> 00:22:00.200
That you love me

00:22:00.640 --> 00:22:02.160
And want to take the blame for me.

00:22:02.160 --> 00:22:04.360
But you really knew nothing about this.

00:22:05.070 --> 00:22:08.280
Your Majesty, I did all this alone.

00:22:08.920 --> 00:22:10.030
Please punish me.

00:22:10.270 --> 00:22:11.030
Good.

00:22:12.110 --> 00:22:14.510
What a deep bond between brother and sister.

00:22:14.510 --> 00:22:16.040
Then I will grant your wish.

00:22:16.270 --> 00:22:18.070
Prince Qi failed in his duty of supervision

00:22:18.070 --> 00:22:19.640
And will receive 30 strokes of the cane.

00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:23.500
Princess Pingning will take the punishment on behalf of her brother.

00:22:26.750 --> 00:22:27.950
Mercy, Your Majesty!

00:22:29.750 --> 00:22:30.950
Mercy, Your Majesty!

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:34.040
You can't do this, Your Majesty!

00:22:34.110 --> 00:22:34.910
Your Majesty!

00:22:35.400 --> 00:22:36.200
Your Majesty!

00:22:36.640 --> 00:22:38.440
You can't do this, Your Majesty!

00:22:38.880 --> 00:22:40.210
-Lejun. -Pass my order.

00:22:40.350 --> 00:22:42.030
Princess Pingning, Li Lejun,

00:22:42.350 --> 00:22:43.830
With the rites of a princess,

00:22:43.830 --> 00:22:46.230
Shall marry the Eagle King of Northern Qin.

00:22:46.400 --> 00:22:48.200
She is the pillar of our diplomatic relations

00:22:48.200 --> 00:22:50.000
And the core of the peace treaty.

00:22:50.030 --> 00:22:53.560
Let the people of Jiankang decorate with flowers and lanterns,

00:22:53.720 --> 00:22:55.000
Sweep the streets,

00:22:55.440 --> 00:22:57.790
And celebrate the grand ceremony of her royal carriage's departure,

00:22:57.790 --> 00:23:01.590
To manifest the virtue of eternal peace between the North and South.

00:23:01.890 --> 00:23:02.610
-Yes. -Yes.

00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:29.770
Your Highness, are you here for the political marriage?

00:23:29.770 --> 00:23:32.170
Your Highness, I beg you to spare my sister.

00:23:33.270 --> 00:23:34.130
Your Highness.

00:23:34.830 --> 00:23:36.830
Look at who these people are first.

00:23:37.400 --> 00:23:39.240
These two are spies sent by you.

00:23:39.920 --> 00:23:41.920
For a bite of food and a sip of water,

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:44.240
They live like beasts of burden.

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:46.510
If your Southern Ye and our Northern Qin form a political marriage,

00:23:46.510 --> 00:23:47.400
These people

00:23:47.790 --> 00:23:49.720
Might live more like human beings.

00:23:50.160 --> 00:23:51.220
So, Your Highness,

00:23:51.270 --> 00:23:54.200
Between Princess Pingning and the beasts of burden,

00:23:54.400 --> 00:23:55.600
Who would you choose?

00:23:57.400 --> 00:23:59.720
And who would Xiao Wuyi choose?

00:24:00.360 --> 00:24:02.090
But why does it have to be Lejun?

00:24:02.550 --> 00:24:03.550
The political marriage

00:24:03.550 --> 00:24:05.830
Was not in the terms of the peace talks in the first place.

00:24:05.830 --> 00:24:07.160
I lost the competition,

00:24:07.480 --> 00:24:08.680
And I am very unhappy.

00:24:09.790 --> 00:24:11.480
That day, the Empress Dowager of your Southern Ye

00:24:11.480 --> 00:24:12.830
Prepared poison arrows,

00:24:12.830 --> 00:24:14.490
Which was truly disgraceful.

00:24:14.680 --> 00:24:16.810
But your sister is quite interesting.

00:24:17.000 --> 00:24:18.130
She broke the arrow.

00:24:18.350 --> 00:24:19.480
Even though she was in deep trouble,

00:24:19.480 --> 00:24:21.030
She still wanted to save others.

00:24:21.030 --> 00:24:22.440
Shouldn't such a stubborn flower

00:24:22.440 --> 00:24:24.680
Bloom in the north wind,

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:25.590
Should it?

00:24:33.380 --> 00:24:33.820
You...

00:24:35.720 --> 00:24:36.780
What are you doing?

00:24:37.270 --> 00:24:38.800
You're in the capital of Ye.

00:24:43.070 --> 00:24:45.270
Who can prove they are from Southern Ye?

00:24:45.920 --> 00:24:48.250
Negotiations require bargaining chips.

00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:49.810
In Northern Qin,

00:24:49.920 --> 00:24:51.720
We respect heroes like Xiao Wuyi

00:24:51.830 --> 00:24:54.590
Who have waded through mountains of swords and seas of blood.

00:24:54.590 --> 00:24:56.400
If he twists the truth out of thin air,

00:24:56.400 --> 00:24:59.330
Who would dare to disagree in your Southern Ye court?

00:25:03.880 --> 00:25:04.920
So, Prince Qi,

00:25:06.310 --> 00:25:07.310
What do you have?

00:25:08.640 --> 00:25:10.770
You are just an empty shell of a Regent,

00:25:12.840 --> 00:25:14.370
Unfit to negotiate with me.

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:18.500
I will not let my sister marry you.

00:25:35.400 --> 00:25:36.730
The day I became Regent,

00:25:37.750 --> 00:25:39.280
Who was the one who chose me?

00:25:39.350 --> 00:25:40.550
Was it His Majesty

00:25:42.200 --> 00:25:43.070
Or you, Master?

00:25:44.600 --> 00:25:45.600
It was me.

00:25:48.550 --> 00:25:51.790
Your Highness, can you tell me today

00:25:53.070 --> 00:25:55.070
If I made the wrong choice?

00:25:59.830 --> 00:26:01.310
What I learned in the past

00:26:02.310 --> 00:26:03.640
Was all about the way of a gentleman

00:26:03.640 --> 00:26:05.300
And the principles of living.

00:26:05.680 --> 00:26:06.640
From now on,

00:26:07.550 --> 00:26:09.880
Please teach me the way of a ruler

00:26:10.550 --> 00:26:11.950
And the art of an emperor.

00:26:13.110 --> 00:26:15.110
Have you really thought it through,

00:26:15.640 --> 00:26:16.970
Not to leave with Jiayu?

00:26:21.520 --> 00:26:22.980
As long as I can save Lejun.

00:26:25.920 --> 00:26:29.640
This path is destined to only go forward,

00:26:31.160 --> 00:26:32.360
With no turning back.

00:26:35.200 --> 00:26:37.000
What is sincerity worth anyway?

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:39.000
How dare you come here and bargain with me?

00:26:39.000 --> 00:26:40.590
Everything you have now

00:26:41.030 --> 00:26:43.430
Was bestowed upon you by His Majesty and me.

00:26:44.460 --> 00:26:45.860
If I decide not to give it,

00:26:46.310 --> 00:26:47.910
Then you shall have nothing.

00:26:51.510 --> 00:26:52.710
I want to have power.

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:55.790
I don't want to be empty-handed anymore,

00:26:55.790 --> 00:26:57.050
Threatened by others,

00:26:57.440 --> 00:26:58.500
And at their mercy.

00:27:07.580 --> 00:27:09.640
You and I both know well what Xiao Wuyi

00:27:09.960 --> 00:27:12.220
Aims to achieve with his reform of Beifu.

00:27:12.640 --> 00:27:14.310
The peace talks are temporary.

00:27:14.310 --> 00:27:16.000
You're just taking advantage of the fact

00:27:16.000 --> 00:27:17.510
That Northern Qin is currently in political chaos

00:27:17.510 --> 00:27:19.440
To gain some breathing room, aren't you?

00:27:19.440 --> 00:27:22.110
If Xiao Wuyi really succeeds in the reform

00:27:22.110 --> 00:27:23.880
And centralizes military power,

00:27:23.880 --> 00:27:25.960
It will weaken the power of your noble families

00:27:25.960 --> 00:27:28.020
And pose a threat to our Northern Qin.

00:27:28.480 --> 00:27:29.720
So, reasonably speaking,

00:27:29.720 --> 00:27:31.070
We should cooperate.

00:27:33.750 --> 00:27:35.920
You want me to commit treason?

00:27:36.910 --> 00:27:39.740
Your Highness, having tea is fine,

00:27:40.640 --> 00:27:43.400
But your appetite is too big.

00:27:44.720 --> 00:27:46.880
And you can't give me what I want.

00:27:47.550 --> 00:27:48.640
What do you want?

00:27:48.920 --> 00:27:50.160
The truth about

00:27:51.270 --> 00:27:53.240
The treason case involving the An and Lu families

00:27:53.240 --> 00:27:54.880
Of Ye 25 years ago.

00:27:59.920 --> 00:28:01.380
I can't help you with that.

00:28:01.440 --> 00:28:03.030
I was just a child back then.

00:28:03.510 --> 00:28:05.920
Let the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin come talk to me.

00:28:05.920 --> 00:28:07.120
She's in the Capital.

00:28:09.070 --> 00:28:09.750
Is she?

00:28:11.510 --> 00:28:12.840
Where else would she be?

00:28:15.030 --> 00:28:17.920
I can give you another greeting gift

00:28:18.110 --> 00:28:20.170
To show my sincerity in cooperation.

00:28:27.160 --> 00:28:27.760
Xiao Wuyi.

00:28:29.350 --> 00:28:31.440
Whether the peace talks succeed or not,

00:28:31.440 --> 00:28:32.700
Li Lejun cannot marry.

00:28:32.880 --> 00:28:34.230
The peace talks must succeed.

00:28:34.230 --> 00:28:35.290
I'm not asking you.

00:28:35.550 --> 00:28:37.810
I'm just telling you what I'm going to do.

00:28:37.880 --> 00:28:39.830
I know what the peace talks mean to you.

00:28:39.830 --> 00:28:41.630
But Lejun is more important to me

00:28:42.270 --> 00:28:43.510
Than anyone else.

00:28:55.590 --> 00:28:57.170
Your Highness, you should tell Prince Qi

00:28:57.170 --> 00:28:59.370
That you're already figuring out a way.

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:02.600
The rift has already formed.

00:29:03.920 --> 00:29:05.450
There's no need to say more.

00:29:06.640 --> 00:29:09.210
[Xiyue Restaurant]

00:29:09.010 --> 00:29:11.030
How is the investigation of the Northern Qin delegation going?

00:29:11.030 --> 00:29:12.310
As you ordered, Your Highness,

00:29:12.310 --> 00:29:14.110
I sent people to keep a close eye on Honglu Temple.

00:29:14.110 --> 00:29:15.720
I also bought the night soil collector off.

00:29:15.720 --> 00:29:17.350
Judging from the medicine dregs,

00:29:17.350 --> 00:29:20.080
Someone in the delegation must be seriously ill,

00:29:20.270 --> 00:29:22.110
And it's an elderly woman.

00:29:22.480 --> 00:29:23.960
Her status is quite high.

00:29:31.870 --> 00:29:33.330
Northwestern tiger bone.

00:29:33.720 --> 00:29:34.780
Liaoshan ginseng.

00:29:39.440 --> 00:29:40.570
South Sea agarwood.

00:29:40.830 --> 00:29:41.760
Quite precious.

00:29:42.510 --> 00:29:44.670
This woman must have an extraordinary identity.

00:29:44.670 --> 00:29:45.700
High status,

00:29:45.720 --> 00:29:47.580
Yet not on the delegation's list.

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:49.790
Either the person's identity is inconvenient to reveal,

00:29:49.790 --> 00:29:51.310
Or their purpose is.

00:29:52.510 --> 00:29:54.070
Is this the great merit you mentioned?

00:29:54.070 --> 00:29:54.870
There's more.

00:29:55.350 --> 00:29:56.920
I had people watch for several days

00:29:56.920 --> 00:29:58.160
Before finally catching up with these two

00:29:58.160 --> 00:30:00.270
Northern Qin people who went to the clinic to buy medicine.

00:30:00.270 --> 00:30:01.480
Here comes the interesting part.

00:30:01.480 --> 00:30:02.400
Guess what?

00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:04.200
These two Northern Qin people

00:30:04.200 --> 00:30:06.160
-look familiar— -Spare me your storytelling.

00:30:06.160 --> 00:30:07.090
Get to the point.

00:30:07.200 --> 00:30:08.800
These two were once at Xiyue Restaurant,

00:30:08.800 --> 00:30:09.900
Listening for several days

00:30:09.900 --> 00:30:11.640
To the storybooks of Crown Prince Wenxi.

00:30:11.640 --> 00:30:13.200
They also sent people to inquire

00:30:13.200 --> 00:30:16.200
About Crown Prince Wenxi and the Phoenix Heart Token.

00:30:17.640 --> 00:30:18.400
Great.

00:30:19.310 --> 00:30:20.600
If the mountain won't come to me,

00:30:20.600 --> 00:30:22.000
I will go to the mountain.

00:30:22.260 --> 00:30:24.990
I'll use the Phoenix Heart Token to draw them out.

00:30:27.030 --> 00:30:30.160
Have Honglu Temple reorganize the peace talk proposals.

00:30:30.160 --> 00:30:31.440
Apart from the three prefectures,

00:30:31.440 --> 00:30:33.700
See if there is any room for negotiation.

00:30:33.700 --> 00:30:36.030
The Eagle King just wants to prove a point.

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:38.720
The Eagle King has always wanted the smelting technique for refined iron,

00:30:38.720 --> 00:30:41.120
Even offering 800 fine horses in exchange.

00:30:41.640 --> 00:30:43.040
This is non-negotiable.

00:31:00.120 --> 00:31:00.800
Spit it out.

00:31:03.880 --> 00:31:04.680
Spit what out?

00:31:04.720 --> 00:31:05.720
Words to scold me.

00:31:06.240 --> 00:31:07.770
Haven't you heard the news?

00:31:09.640 --> 00:31:11.920
I did have a lot to say to scold you.

00:31:14.110 --> 00:31:16.240
But you look so weighed down with troubles.

00:31:16.240 --> 00:31:16.900
Never mind.

00:31:23.310 --> 00:31:24.240
What did Mao say?

00:31:25.450 --> 00:31:29.050
He won't let Li Lejun enter a political marriage, no matter what,

00:31:30.000 --> 00:31:31.350
At any cost.

00:31:32.140 --> 00:31:34.070
Mao and Lejun only have each other.

00:31:34.830 --> 00:31:36.560
It's only right for him to do so.

00:31:38.110 --> 00:31:39.510
But to you, Xiao Wuyi,

00:31:40.510 --> 00:31:42.570
Ensuring the peace talks go smoothly

00:31:42.720 --> 00:31:44.720
And buying time for the Beifu reform

00:31:45.350 --> 00:31:47.080
Are the most important things.

00:31:51.640 --> 00:31:52.240
Yes.

00:31:53.030 --> 00:31:53.790
Though,

00:31:55.350 --> 00:31:57.010
You know what Lejun will face.

00:32:05.510 --> 00:32:06.110
All right.

00:32:09.640 --> 00:32:10.240
That's it?

00:32:11.910 --> 00:32:14.220
I thought you would argue with me,

00:32:15.640 --> 00:32:17.790
Calling me a liar, cold-blooded,

00:32:18.720 --> 00:32:19.980
And worse than a beast.

00:32:21.230 --> 00:32:22.030
Xiao Wuyi,

00:32:22.310 --> 00:32:23.400
In your heart,

00:32:23.590 --> 00:32:25.110
Am I that unreasonable?

00:32:25.110 --> 00:32:27.240
Have you ever been reasonable with me?

00:32:35.230 --> 00:32:37.960
You have already changed Lejun's birth records.

00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:39.880
You've done all you can.

00:32:40.550 --> 00:32:42.750
The instigator today is the Eagle King.

00:32:43.110 --> 00:32:44.570
You only made your choice.

00:32:46.680 --> 00:32:47.810
You are not to blame.

00:32:54.160 --> 00:32:55.470
What's with that look?

00:32:57.440 --> 00:32:58.070
Nothing.

00:32:58.440 --> 00:32:59.400
I don't know either.

00:32:59.400 --> 00:33:00.480
Probably because

00:33:01.270 --> 00:33:03.930
It's the first time I've heard someone say that,

00:33:04.310 --> 00:33:05.310
So it feels fresh.

00:33:06.510 --> 00:33:07.110
However,

00:33:08.270 --> 00:33:09.830
I will still stop this.

00:33:11.920 --> 00:33:13.780
If Lejun were a pampered princess

00:33:14.680 --> 00:33:16.080
Supported by the people,

00:33:16.880 --> 00:33:19.160
Then she would shoulder the responsibility of the world now,

00:33:19.160 --> 00:33:20.690
And I'd have nothing to say.

00:33:20.990 --> 00:33:21.840
But she is not.

00:33:26.310 --> 00:33:27.240
Qizhou fell.

00:33:28.640 --> 00:33:30.240
Mao and Lejun fled all the way

00:33:31.070 --> 00:33:32.000
To Jiankang.

00:33:32.790 --> 00:33:33.550
Did His Majesty and Her Majesty

00:33:33.550 --> 00:33:35.480
Ever care for them for a single day?

00:33:36.480 --> 00:33:38.720
They only have the status of the royal family in name,

00:33:38.720 --> 00:33:40.780
But live worse than ordinary people.

00:33:41.240 --> 00:33:42.500
To support the family,

00:33:42.590 --> 00:33:44.790
Lejun has been copying books for others

00:33:44.790 --> 00:33:46.720
And doing needlework since childhood.

00:33:46.720 --> 00:33:48.070
She was already weak.

00:33:48.920 --> 00:33:51.200
If my mother hadn't known some medical skills

00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:53.200
And hadn't found out Lejun had an old illness,

00:33:53.200 --> 00:33:55.000
She would have barely survived.

00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:58.380
This is not the ending a good person should have.

00:34:01.030 --> 00:34:02.640
How do you plan to stop it?

00:34:03.270 --> 00:34:04.000
Don't worry.

00:34:05.310 --> 00:34:06.270
My method

00:34:07.200 --> 00:34:09.130
Has nothing to do with your empire.

00:34:13.320 --> 00:34:14.320
Being your friend

00:34:16.030 --> 00:34:16.889
Is quite lucky.

00:34:20.710 --> 00:34:21.370
You forgot.

00:34:24.590 --> 00:34:25.850
You are also my friend.

00:35:01.700 --> 00:35:05.120
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

00:35:05.420 --> 00:35:09.090
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:07.410
I'm here to save you!

00:35:09.200 --> 00:35:13.570
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

00:35:13.930 --> 00:35:16.620
♪ So desolate ♪

00:35:17.200 --> 00:35:20.870
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

00:35:19.760 --> 00:35:20.840
Someone like you

00:35:20.900 --> 00:35:24.440
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

00:35:21.440 --> 00:35:23.240
Is born to be on the battlefield,

00:35:23.540 --> 00:35:24.760
To make everyone fear you.

00:35:24.620 --> 00:35:29.960
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

00:35:30.600 --> 00:35:34.040
♪ If the heavens should change and fate tear me apart ♪

00:35:34.060 --> 00:35:38.060
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat of my heart's art ♪

00:35:38.200 --> 00:35:41.910
♪ I've traveled so far— the day I find you again ♪

00:35:41.930 --> 00:35:45.630
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

00:35:44.230 --> 00:35:45.230
If you trust me,

00:35:45.880 --> 00:35:48.700
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

00:35:46.200 --> 00:35:47.260
Let me be your eyes.

00:35:48.730 --> 00:35:51.220
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

00:35:51.490 --> 00:35:55.650
♪ Apart from you, the world is an endless night ♪

00:35:55.670 --> 00:35:59.270
♪ Even if my beating heart wears thin and fades ♪

00:35:59.520 --> 00:36:01.290
♪ I'd choose this fate till death's final line ♪

00:36:00.110 --> 00:36:00.770
You forgot.

00:36:01.280 --> 00:36:02.150
You are also my friend.

00:36:01.520 --> 00:36:04.140
♪ I only hope the mortal lands ♪

00:36:04.170 --> 00:36:06.830
♪ Can grant our wishes ♪

00:36:04.360 --> 00:36:05.760
It's quite hard to let go.

00:36:07.090 --> 00:36:11.330
♪ Through endless night, let heaven and earth fall apart ♪

00:36:11.660 --> 00:36:15.830
♪ I'd bid farewell to every worldly part ♪

00:36:16.140 --> 00:36:20.980
♪ Just to gaze upon you one last time ♪

00:36:31.840 --> 00:36:33.510
Have you done what I told you?

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:35.110
As you instructed, My Lady,

00:36:35.110 --> 00:36:37.030
The item has been delivered to the Eagle King.

00:36:37.030 --> 00:36:37.510
Good.

00:36:38.150 --> 00:36:39.360
If anyone asks later,

00:36:39.380 --> 00:36:41.070
Just say I went to the South Street Bookstore

00:36:41.070 --> 00:36:42.280
To buy books for Yuanji.

00:36:42.280 --> 00:36:43.400
You don't know anything else.

00:36:43.400 --> 00:36:46.130
-Especially don't let Xiao Wuyi know. -Morning.

00:36:50.510 --> 00:36:51.210
What are you doing?

00:36:51.210 --> 00:36:52.340
Where are you going?

00:36:52.510 --> 00:36:53.480
First to the South Street Bookstore

00:36:53.480 --> 00:36:54.630
To buy books for Yuanji,

00:36:54.630 --> 00:36:55.480
Then to Renhe Hall

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:57.190
To fetch the newly arrived cassia seeds for Ruisheng.

00:36:57.190 --> 00:36:58.230
After that, to Xinghua Restaurant

00:36:58.230 --> 00:36:59.690
To buy mint cakes for Ziqi.

00:37:01.770 --> 00:37:03.510
What about you? Where are you going?

00:37:03.510 --> 00:37:04.240
To the palace

00:37:05.000 --> 00:37:08.070
To continue discussing the peace talks with Northern Qin.

00:37:08.070 --> 00:37:09.150
After you.

00:37:09.510 --> 00:37:10.710
Your business is more important.

00:37:10.710 --> 00:37:11.770
I won't bother you.

00:37:19.090 --> 00:37:21.640
[Xiyue Restaurant]

00:37:22.630 --> 00:37:24.320
-Great! -Great!

00:37:28.510 --> 00:37:29.670
During the storytelling just now,

00:37:29.670 --> 00:37:31.880
You said you had seen the Phoenix Heart Token.

00:37:31.880 --> 00:37:32.710
Of course.

00:37:33.670 --> 00:37:34.550
Come with me.

00:37:36.290 --> 00:37:38.630
[Honglu Temple]

00:37:41.920 --> 00:37:43.590
Xiao Wuyi's little beauty.

00:37:44.480 --> 00:37:45.480
What a rare guest.

00:37:47.030 --> 00:37:49.630
You sent someone to deliver refined iron to me.

00:37:49.760 --> 00:37:51.290
What's the meaning of this?

00:37:52.190 --> 00:37:53.590
Where did this come from?

00:37:53.630 --> 00:37:54.360
I smelted it.

00:37:56.230 --> 00:37:57.550
First, forged at a high temperature

00:37:57.550 --> 00:37:58.800
To remove all impurities,

00:37:58.800 --> 00:38:00.530
Then quenched in green liquor.

00:38:01.840 --> 00:38:02.440
I know

00:38:03.030 --> 00:38:05.830
You want the smelting technique for refined iron.

00:38:09.590 --> 00:38:12.250
Are you really going to give me the refined iron?

00:38:12.480 --> 00:38:13.230
Not exactly.

00:38:13.230 --> 00:38:14.590
I just used this refined iron as bait

00:38:14.590 --> 00:38:15.800
To lure you to meet me.

00:38:18.510 --> 00:38:19.570
Are you playing me?

00:38:19.890 --> 00:38:20.820
I wouldn't dare.

00:38:21.510 --> 00:38:23.710
Princess Pingning is my close friend.

00:38:25.940 --> 00:38:27.260
So it's about this.

00:38:28.590 --> 00:38:30.920
I didn't expect Princess Pingning's life

00:38:31.440 --> 00:38:32.640
To be quite valuable.

00:38:33.400 --> 00:38:34.840
You want to marry Pingning

00:38:34.840 --> 00:38:36.230
Just to vent your anger

00:38:36.480 --> 00:38:37.610
And regain dignity.

00:38:38.670 --> 00:38:42.330
If you are interested in the smelting technique for refined iron,

00:38:43.550 --> 00:38:45.210
Then I'll make a deal with you.

00:38:45.400 --> 00:38:45.770
No,

00:38:47.000 --> 00:38:47.660
A business.

00:38:51.000 --> 00:38:52.000
I'm all ears.

00:39:08.360 --> 00:39:09.160
Your Majesty.

00:39:09.650 --> 00:39:12.850
[Shao Yang, the Empress Dowager of the Northern Qin]

00:39:10.110 --> 00:39:11.710
I've heard so much about you.

00:39:16.320 --> 00:39:18.450
I thought I caught someone's slip-up,

00:39:20.840 --> 00:39:21.900
But I didn't expect

00:39:22.440 --> 00:39:24.280
That it was I who made a mistake.

00:39:25.000 --> 00:39:26.800
Your Highness, if you hadn't

00:39:27.000 --> 00:39:29.530
Eliminated Northern Qin's spy strongholds,

00:39:30.960 --> 00:39:32.150
These two fools

00:39:33.920 --> 00:39:36.840
Wouldn't have been discovered so easily.

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:39.780
Being a spy

00:39:41.230 --> 00:39:43.030
Still needs experience.

00:39:43.480 --> 00:39:45.480
Why did you come here, Your Majesty?

00:39:46.150 --> 00:39:48.280
Is it also for the Phoenix Heart Token?

00:39:49.670 --> 00:39:50.670
If I say

00:39:51.670 --> 00:39:53.070
I got tired of the Capital

00:39:53.800 --> 00:39:56.070
And came to Southern Ye to enjoy the scenery,

00:39:56.070 --> 00:39:57.200
Will you believe me?

00:39:58.230 --> 00:39:59.030
I won't.

00:40:01.890 --> 00:40:03.820
Then that's the only excuse I have.

00:40:05.510 --> 00:40:06.360
Speak.

00:40:07.000 --> 00:40:09.260
Your Highness, why did you want to see me?

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:11.280
Are you trying to tell me

00:40:11.280 --> 00:40:13.070
Where the Phoenix Heart Token is?

00:40:13.070 --> 00:40:14.870
I hope you can stop the Eagle King

00:40:14.920 --> 00:40:16.850
From marrying Princess Pingning.

00:40:17.550 --> 00:40:21.360
A political marriage between Northern Qin and Ye is a long-term strategy.

00:40:21.360 --> 00:40:23.560
You have been in the military for years.

00:40:23.920 --> 00:40:25.110
Don't you understand

00:40:25.110 --> 00:40:26.710
That peace benefits both?

00:40:27.110 --> 00:40:28.760
You must know better than I do

00:40:29.840 --> 00:40:31.480
That the emperor of Northern Qin and the Eagle King

00:40:31.480 --> 00:40:33.590
Are only sovereign and subject on the surface.

00:40:33.590 --> 00:40:35.110
The Eagle King has heavily armed himself,

00:40:35.110 --> 00:40:36.670
And you support the emperor.

00:40:36.670 --> 00:40:39.130
That's why the Northern Qin court is stable.

00:40:40.440 --> 00:40:42.000
But if you pass away

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:44.510
And the Eagle King forms a marriage alliance with Ye,

00:40:44.510 --> 00:40:45.840
Marrying the sister of the current Regent,

00:40:45.840 --> 00:40:47.230
Prince Qi,

00:40:47.840 --> 00:40:49.440
Once he has Jiankang's help,

00:40:49.670 --> 00:40:51.200
The balance will be broken.

00:40:52.030 --> 00:40:52.760
In that case,

00:40:53.480 --> 00:40:54.680
How can you guarantee

00:40:55.030 --> 00:40:56.360
The Eagle King's troops

00:40:56.590 --> 00:40:58.590
Will still be Northern Qin's sword?

00:41:04.000 --> 00:41:05.630
You make a valid point.

00:41:08.000 --> 00:41:11.330
But even if my son and I have disagreements with the Eagle King,

00:41:11.330 --> 00:41:13.530
It's not for an outsider to manipulate.

00:41:14.630 --> 00:41:16.830
Such an obvious attempt to sow discord—

00:41:17.550 --> 00:41:19.510
Are you being too impatient?

00:41:21.360 --> 00:41:22.420
Just a suggestion.

00:41:33.280 --> 00:41:34.080
Your Majesty.

00:41:40.440 --> 00:41:42.900
Thank you for your kindness, Your Highness.

00:41:43.000 --> 00:41:45.440
Then I will also tell you something.

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:48.480
Your Secondary Consort, Xie Jiayu,

00:41:48.590 --> 00:41:50.190
For the political marriage,

00:41:50.920 --> 00:41:54.150
Is secretly meeting the Eagle King at Honglu Temple right now.

00:41:54.150 --> 00:41:55.000
I heard

00:41:55.880 --> 00:41:58.480
She also prepared a big gift for the Eagle King.

00:42:02.360 --> 00:42:03.760
Please wait, Your Highness.

00:42:03.760 --> 00:42:05.220
I have shown my sincerity.

00:42:05.290 --> 00:42:07.670
I hope you can carefully consider the political marriage

00:42:07.670 --> 00:42:09.200
And make a good deal with me.

00:42:09.670 --> 00:42:11.440
I'll await your good news.

00:42:12.840 --> 00:42:13.900
I won't see you out.

00:42:19.530 --> 00:42:21.130
No need to see me out. Go back.

00:42:24.200 --> 00:42:24.990
Excuse me.

00:42:27.630 --> 00:42:28.430
Still acting?

00:42:30.320 --> 00:42:33.230
Since when has the South Street Bookstore been open in Honglu Temple?

00:42:33.230 --> 00:42:35.480
Well, I was just...

